  "title": "SearchOS-V1: Towards Robust Open-Domain Information-Seeking Agent Collaboration",
  "summary": "SearchOS externalizes multi-agent research state into a task frontier, evidence graph, coverage map, and failure memory. Its scheduler and middleware use those structures to reduce repeated searches and detect stalls, treating research reliability as a state-management problem.",
